Class Card

  • java.lang.Object
    • Card

  • public class Card
extends java.lang.Object
    An immutable class representing a card from a normal 52-card deck.

    • Method Detail

      • fromString

        public static Card fromString(java.lang.String string)
        Create a new Card instance from the given string. The string should be a two-character string where the first character is the rank and the second character is the suit. For example, "Kc" means the king of clubs, and "As" means the ace of spades.
        Parameters:
        string - Card to create as a string.
        Returns:
        a new Card instance corresponding to the given string.
